citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:10pm on
February 29, 2024.
Upon arrival to the facility, the inspector attempted to contact the licensee and facility representative via the phone
numbers on file, leaving a voicemail message for the facility representative. The licensee’s voicemail mailbox was full.
The inspector waited 30 minutes before leaving the facility. Upon leaving the facility, the inspector spoke with the licensee
by phone, stating their earliest availability for an inspection would be hours later at minimum.
End Section
